  "texts": [
    "In this method, the character embeddings and the CNN network all are shared between NER and word segmentation models.Implementation details.",
    "We use Keras 2.2.4 and Tensorflow 1.14 to implement our model in Windows 10 within 2080 Ti GPU.",
    "The embedding dimension of each character is 128, and the sentence length is uniform at 100 characters.",
    "The redundant parts of sentences with more than 100 characters are removed, and the sentences with less than 100 characters are padded with zeros.",
    "There are three convolution layers, and the dilation factor δ i is set to 1, 2, and 4, respectively."
  ],
